	   <tr><td colspan=2>One comment to add.&nbsp;&nbsp;Aggro is as much a function of range to mob as anything else.  If you don't want aggro, fight at maximum melee range.  Fight behind the tank till you get comfortable with judging range, then move behind mob to avoid its ripostes.  Just remember to keep backing up as the tank pushes the mob.<br><br>If you WANT aggro, stand on the mob's toes.<br>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke<br>Member of Tenacity - Druzzil Ro<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a></td></tr>
